<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/sly" style="color:black;">sly</a>, <a href="/dictionary/cunning" style="color:black;">cunning</a>, <a href="/dictionary/shrewd" style="color:black;">shrewd</a>; artful</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 18<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 18 strokes: <a href="/character/翻" title="fan1: flip over, upset, capsize">翻</a>, <a href="/character/覆" title="fu4: cover; tip over; return; reply">覆</a>, <a href="/character/鹰" title="ying1: falcon; Accipiter species (various)">鹰</a>, <a href="/character/藤" title="teng2: rattan, cane; creeper plant">藤</a>, <a href="/character/鞭" title="bian1: whip; whip; string of firecrackers">鞭</a>, <a href="/character/藩" title="fan1: fence; boundary; outlying border">藩</a>, <a href="/character/鳍" title="qi2: fin">鳍</a>, <a href="/character/蹦" title="beng4: hop, leap, jump; bright">蹦</a>, <a href="/character/襟" title="jin1: lapel, collar">襟</a>, <a href="/character/戳" title="chuo1: prick, stab; stamp, seal, chop">戳</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/黑" title="Kangxi radical 203">黑</a>&nbsp;203.6</p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 4160</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 6340</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/狡黠" title="jiao3 xia2">狡黠</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">黠[<span style="color:#cc7700;">xiá</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- (phonetic)<br>- crafty<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+9EE0</p></div>

